            🚢 PirateShip:
               Name: %s
               Type: %s
               Cannons: %d
               Crew capacity: %d
               Has sails: %s
               Has Jolly Roger: %s
               Captain: %s
               Cargo: %d tons
               Home port: %s
            """, name, type, cannons, crewCapacity, hasSails,
                hasJollyRoger, captainName, cargoCapacity, homePort);
